snippet.textDisplay: I felt this song so touchy. This is awesome, in all respect. I salute coke studio, MTv, by heart,to encourage and upload this song. The lyrics of the song has infinite sense to touch,understand and involve God, the world and the word. The composer  and the singer have excellently done their match, to automatically bring tears from their own and the listeners eyes. I have really wept withot wiping my tears. My tears kept on flowing and I repeatedly kept on listening with the excellent melody,the voice of DEAR KAILAS  AND HIS PERFORMANCE.and  swayed with this heart touching and stirring song. I love this song,the composer, the writer and THE SINGER KAILAS........KAILAS........KAILAS. I salute the coments from Dipti Mehta, Parth Prajapati,Payal Jethwa, Maja L, Rajiv Khare, Emilly Exodius for their feelings for such a great and devine song.  CHALO HAM SAB MILKE GAYE EK SAATH......ANAAHAD  NAAD  BAJAAORI SAB MIL , ANAHAD  NAAD  BAJAAORI SABMIL.........ANAHAD NAAD BAJAAORI  SABMIL........
